# Breadcrumb

Navigation trail that shows hierarchy.

## Basic Usage
::TuffDemo{title="Breadcrumb Trail" description="Provide a quick sense of place." code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <template>
    <TxBreadcrumb
      :items="[
        { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
        { label: 'Library', href: '/library' },
        { label: 'Data' },
      ]"
    />
  </template>
---
